0627","numberInSurah":15,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"quran-simple","language":"ar","name":"Simple","englishName":"Simple","format":"text","type":"quran"}},{"number":91,"name":"\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0645\u0633","englishName":"Ash-Shams","englishNameTranslation":"The Sun","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":15,"ayahs":[{"text":"In the name of God, The Most Gracious, The Dispenser of Grace:"},{"number":6044,"text":"CONSIDER the sun and its radiant brightness,","numberInSurah":1,"juz":30},{"number":6045,"text":"and the moon as it reflects the sun!","numberInSurah":2,"juz":30},{"number":6046,"text":"Consider the day as it reveals the world,","numberInSurah":3,"juz":30},{"number":6047,"text":"and the night as it veils it darkly!","numberInSurah":4,"juz":30},{"number":6048,"text":"Consider the sky and its wondrous make,","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30},{"number":6049,"text":"and the earth and all its expanse!","numberInSurah":6,"juz":30},{"number":6050,"text":"Consider the human self, and how it is formed in accordance with what it is meant to be,","numberInSurah":7,"juz":30},{"number":6051,"text":"and how it is imbued with moral failings as well as with consciousness of God!","numberInSurah":8,"juz":30},{"number":6052,"text":"To a happy state shall indeed attain he who causes this [self] to grow in purity,","numberInSurah":9,"juz":30},{"number":6053,"text":"and truly lost is he who buries it [in darkness].","numberInSurah":10,"juz":30},{"number":6054,"text":"TO [THIS] TRUTH gave the lie, in their overweening arrogance, [the tribe of] Thamud,","numberInSurah":11,"juz":30},{"number":6055,"text":"when that most hapless wretch from among them rushed forward [to commit his evil deed],","numberInSurah":12,"juz":30},{"number":6056,"text":"although God's apostle had told them, \"It is a she-camel belonging to God, so let her drink [and do her no harm]!\"","numberInSurah":13,"juz":30},{"number":6057,"text":"But they gave him the lie, and cruelly slaughtered her - whereupon their Sustainer visited them with utter destruction for this their sin, destroying them all alike:","numberInSurah":14,"juz":30},{"number":6058,"text":"for none [of them] had any fear of what might befall them.","numberInSurah":15,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"en.asad","language":"en","name":"Asad","englishName":"Muhammad Asad","format":"text","type":"translation"}}]}